title: [Warrior Guild, Southern Grove]
description: A glance to the north or south reveals nothing but a wall of very tall trees.  Sunlight angles in from overhead, creating long shadows across the grassy pathway.  A simple rope swing dangles from one of the thicker branches, oddly out of place in this training center.

A glance to the north or south reveals nothing but a wall of very tall trees.  A simple rope swing dangles from one of the thicker branches, illuminated by soft moonlight angling in from overhead.  It seems a bit out of place in this center of martial training.
